530
01:08:44,433 --> 01:08:47,346
Human decisions are removed
from strategic defence.

531
01:08:47,561 --> 01:08:50,269
Skynet begins to learn at a geometric rate.

532
01:08:50,481 --> 01:08:54,646
It becomes self-aware at 02:14am
Eastern time, August 29.

533
01:08:55,820 --> 01:08:58,153
