575
01:12:38,334 --> 01:12:39,290
Excellent.

576
01:12:50,137 --> 01:12:53,676
This is my best truck I got,
but the starter motor's gone.

577
01:12:53,891 --> 01:12:55,678
You got time to change it out?

578
01:12:55,893 --> 01:12:58,931
Yeah. I'm gonna wait till dark
to cross the border.

579
01:13:01,607 --> 01:13:05,896
See, I grew up in places like this,
so I just thought that's how people lived,

580
01:13:06,111 --> 01:13:10,606
riding around in helicopters,
learning how to blow shit up.

581
01:13:15,496 --> 01:13:17,112
That's definitely you.

582
01:13:28,759 --> 01:13:31,342
Most of the guys my mom
hung around with were geeks,

583
01:13:31,553 --> 01:13:35,217
but there was this one guy,
he was kinda cool.

584
01:13:35,432 --> 01:13:38,596
- He taught me engines.
- Hold here.

585
01:13:39,561 --> 01:13:41,974
Mom screwed it up, of course.

586
01:13:42,189 --> 01:13:44,226
She'd always tell 'em about Judgment Day

587
01:13:44,441 --> 01:13:46,808
and me being this world leader.

588
01:13:47,611 --> 01:13:51,605
- That'd be all she wrote.
- Torque wrench, please.

589
01:13:54,034 --> 01:13:55,115
Here.

590
01:13:56,161 --> 01:14:00,576
- I wish I could've met my real dad.
- You will.

591
01:14:00,791 --> 01:14:05,377
Yeah, I guess. When I'm, like, 45, I think.

592
01:14:06,672 --> 01:14:09,836
I sent him back through time to 1984.

593
01:14:10,676 --> 01:14:11,917
Man!

594
01:14:13,637 --> 01:14:15,924
He hasn't even been born yet.

595
01:14:17,683 --> 01:14:19,640
It messes with your head.

596
01:14:22,271 --> 01:14:24,888
- The other bolt.
- Oh. Here.

597
01:14:31,864 --> 01:14:35,278
Mom and him were only together for one night.

598
01:14:35,492 --> 01:14:40,658
She still loves him, I guess.
I see her crying sometimes.

599
01:14:40,873 --> 01:14:45,287
She denies it totally, of course,
like she got something stuck in her eye.

600
01:14:49,548 --> 01:14:51,039
Why do you cry?

601
01:14:52,176 --> 01:14:53,963
- You mean people?
- Yeah.

602
01:14:54,178 --> 01:14:56,636
I don't know. We just cry.

603
01:14:57,598 --> 01:14:59,931
You know, when it hurts.

604
01:15:06,231 --> 01:15:11,226
- Pain causes it?
- Er... no. It's different.

605
01:15:11,445 --> 01:15:14,404
It's when there's nothing wrong
with you, but you hurt anyways.

606
01:15:14,615 --> 01:15:16,426
- Get it?
- No.

607
01:15:17,409 --> 01:15:18,991
All right, my man!

608
01:15:19,203 --> 01:15:22,412
<i>- No problemo.</i>
- Give me five.

609
01:15:24,958 --> 01:15:26,870
Just put out your hand, like this.

610
01:15:28,253 --> 01:15:31,963
All right! Now hit me.
Give me five. Do the same thing.

611
01:15:32,374 --> 01:15:34,011
All right!

612
01:15:37,137 --> 01:15:39,470
Okay, that's good. Up high! High five!

613
01:15:40,599 --> 01:15:41,715
Five low.

614
01:15:42,634 --> 01:15:44,125
Too slow.

615
01:15:46,605 --> 01:15:48,722
