616
01:15:48,941 --> 01:15:51,024
Good. Now try it. Good!

617
01:15:51,235 --> 01:15:52,976
Now do me. Give me five.

618
01:15:54,696 --> 01:15:56,688
'Watching John with the machine,

619
01:15:56,907 --> 01:15:59,069
it was suddenly so clear.

620
01:15:59,284 --> 01:16:02,243
'The Terminator would never stop.

621
01:16:02,454 --> 01:16:06,118
'It would never leave him
and it would never hurt him,

622
01:16:06,333 --> 01:16:09,747
'never shout at him or get drunk and hit him

623
01:16:09,962 --> 01:16:12,249
'or say it was too busy
to spend time with him.

624
01:16:13,298 --> 01:16:18,009
'It would always be there
and it would die to protect him.

625
01:16:19,763 --> 01:16:22,756
'Of all the would-be fathers
who came and went over the years,

626
01:16:22,975 --> 01:16:27,310
'this thing, this machine,
was the only one who measured up.

627
01:16:28,313 --> 01:16:32,728
'In an insane world,
it was the sanest choice.'

628
01:17:05,767 --> 01:17:10,603
Come here, darling.

629
01:18:10,374 --> 01:18:12,582
Hey, let's try this one.

630
01:18:17,964 --> 01:18:19,500
There we go.

631
01:20:05,739 --> 01:20:08,152
She said you go south
with him like you planned.

632
01:20:08,366 --> 01:20:11,359
- She'll meet you tomorrow.
- Mom!

633
01:20:11,578 --> 01:20:13,319
Mom, wait!

634
01:20:28,804 --> 01:20:30,511
"No fate".

635
01:20:31,848 --> 01:20:34,056
"No fate, but what we make."

636
01:20:36,228 --> 01:20:37,844
My father told her this.

637
01:20:40,857 --> 01:20:45,443
I mean, I made him memorise it
in the future as a message to her.

638
01:20:46,696 --> 01:20:51,862
Never mind.
Now, okay, the whole thing goes...

639
01:20:52,077 --> 01:20:54,694
The future's not set.

640
01:20:54,913 --> 01:20:58,327
There's no fate,
but what we make for ourselves.

641
01:20:58,542 --> 01:21:03,037
- She intends to change the future.
- Yeah, I guess.

642
01:21:04,506 --> 01:21:06,213
Oh, shit!

643
01:21:06,424 --> 01:21:08,211
- Dyson.
- Yeah.

644
01:21:08,426 --> 01:21:11,794
Gotta be. Miles Dyson.

645
01:21:12,013 --> 01:21:13,879
She's gonna blow him away.

646
01:21:14,099 --> 01:21:15,965
Come on! Let's go!

647
01:21:16,184 --> 01:21:17,846
Let's go! Come on!

648
01:21:28,613 --> 01:21:31,606
- This is tactically dangerous.
- Drive faster.

649
01:21:31,825 --> 01:21:35,569
The T-1000 has the same files
that I do. It knows what I know.

650
01:21:35,787 --> 01:21:40,282
- It might anticipate this move.
- I don't care. We gotta stop her.

651
01:21:40,500 --> 01:21:42,867
Killing Dyson might prevent the war.

652
01:21:43,086 --> 01:21:44,793
I don't care!

653
01:21:45,005 --> 01:21:46,792
Haven't you learned anything yet?

654
01:21:47,007 --> 01:21:49,169
Haven't you figured out
why you can't kill people?

655
01:21:55,390 --> 01:21:57,803
Danny, I told you to go to bed.
I'm not kidding.

656
01:21:58,018 --> 01:22:01,261
Just a couple of minutes, Mom!

657
01:22:09,738 --> 01:22:11,946
Danny, your time is up!

658
01:22:12,157 --> 01:22:14,945
Come brush your teeth and get to bed.

659
01:22:43,688 --> 01:22:44,895
Danny!

660
01:22:56,660 --> 01:23:00,404
- Daddy!
- Danny, just go! Go, Danny! Go!

661
01:23:02,123 --> 01:23:03,159
Miles?

662
01:23:06,920 --> 01:23:08,331
Miles!

663
01:23:08,546 --> 01:23:10,833
- Tarissa, run!
- Oh, my God!

664
01:23:18,056 --> 01:23:19,968
Tarissa, just take Danny and go. Run!

665
01:23:20,183 --> 01:23:21,299
Run!

666
01:23:21,518 --> 01:23:23,134
Oh, Jesus! Miles!

667
01:23:42,497 --> 01:23:44,580
- Daddy!
- Danny! Danny!

668
01:23:44,791 --> 01:23:48,284
- Nobody fucking move!
- Don't hurt my daddy!

669
01:23:48,503 --> 01:23:52,167
Get down on the floor, bitch. Get down now!

670
01:23:52,382 --> 01:23:54,123
Get out of the way.

671
01:23:54,342 --> 01:23:55,924
Don't hurt him!

672
01:23:57,637 --> 01:23:59,173
Get on the floor now!

673
01:24:01,474 --> 01:24:03,932
Just let the boy go.

674
01:24:04,144 --> 01:24:06,978
Shut up. Shut up. Shut up! Shut up!

675
01:24:07,188 --> 01:24:09,646
It's all your fault, motherfucker.

676
01:24:09,858 --> 01:24:11,975
- It's all your fault!
- What?

677
01:24:12,193 --> 01:24:14,185
