678
01:24:32,839 --> 01:24:33,955
Shhh!

679
01:24:38,219 --> 01:24:39,426
Shhh.

680
01:25:06,289 --> 01:25:08,656
Shit! We're too late!

681
01:25:12,879 --> 01:25:13,869
Check them.

682
01:25:17,592 --> 01:25:21,085
Look at me, Mom. Are you hurt?

683
01:25:22,055 --> 01:25:23,591
Look at me.

684
01:25:25,600 --> 01:25:27,557
I almost...

685
01:25:27,769 --> 01:25:29,681
I almost...

686
01:25:39,489 --> 01:25:43,529
It'll be okay. It's gonna be okay.
We'll figure something out. Okay?

687
01:25:45,495 --> 01:25:46,827
I promise.

688
01:25:50,708 --> 01:25:55,874
- You came here to stop me.
- Yeah, I did.

689
01:25:58,967 --> 01:26:00,754
I love you, John.

690
01:26:02,679 --> 01:26:04,762
I always have.

691
01:26:06,224 --> 01:26:08,056
I know.

692
01:26:14,524 --> 01:26:16,561
Deep penetration.

693
01:26:18,319 --> 01:26:20,106
No shattered bone.

694
01:26:20,321 --> 01:26:23,109
You hold here. The pressure
should stop the bleeding.

695
01:26:34,043 --> 01:26:37,207
- Who are you people?
- Show him.

696
01:26:40,508 --> 01:26:44,548
Danny, I want you to come with me
right now. Show me your room.

697
01:26:57,609 --> 01:27:00,727
Oh, God! No!

698
01:27:13,208 --> 01:27:15,495
Oh, my God!

699
01:27:24,761 --> 01:27:26,252
Oh, my God.

700
01:27:26,471 --> 01:27:28,929
Now, listen to me very carefully.

701
01:27:31,351 --> 01:27:34,719
Nuclear winter effects
caused massive cooling...

702
01:27:34,938 --> 01:27:38,978
'Dyson listened while
the Terminator laid it all down.

703
01:27:39,192 --> 01:27:42,776
'Skynet. Judgment Day.

704
01:27:42,987 --> 01:27:46,025
'The history of things to come.

705
01:27:46,991 --> 01:27:52,278
'It's not every day that you find out
you're responsible for three billion deaths.

706
01:27:52,497 --> 01:27:55,080
'He took it pretty well.'

707
01:27:56,501 --> 01:27:59,084
I feel like I'm gonna throw up.

708
01:28:05,593 --> 01:28:10,179
