739
01:29:52,742 --> 01:29:56,444
I mean, it was smashed, it didn't work,
but it gave us ideas,

740
01:29:56,662 --> 01:29:59,530
took us in new directions,
things we would've never th...

741
01:30:01,793 --> 01:30:03,785
