742
01:30:04,003 --> 01:30:05,665
It must be destroyed.

743
01:30:08,007 --> 01:30:10,966
Can you get us in? Past security?

744
01:30:11,177 --> 01:30:14,090
I think so, yeah. When?

745
01:30:18,142 --> 01:30:19,098
Now?

746
01:30:23,356 --> 01:30:26,019
'The future, always so clear to me,

747
01:30:26,234 --> 01:30:29,147
