748
01:30:29,362 --> 01:30:34,903
'We were in uncharted territory now,
making up history as we went along.'

749
01:31:10,361 --> 01:31:14,856
Hi. Er... Carl, right?

750
01:31:16,617 --> 01:31:18,449
Friends from out of town.
I just thought I'd...

751
01:31:18,870 --> 01:31:19,701
Hi!

752
01:31:20,121 --> 01:31:21,987
...take 'em upstairs and show 'em around.

753
01:31:22,206 --> 01:31:25,370
Mr Dyson, you know the rules
concerning visitors in the lab.

754
01:31:25,585 --> 01:31:27,577
I need written authorisation...

755
01:31:28,796 --> 01:31:32,506
- I insist.
